%%{init: {"theme":"base","securityLevel":"strict","deterministicIds":true,"deterministicIDSeed":"lightcode-hosted-auth-v1","themeVariables":{"fontFamily":"Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui","fontSize":"15px","background":"#ffffff","primaryColor":"#f8fafc","primaryTextColor":"#0f172a","primaryBorderColor":"#cbd5e1","secondaryColor":"#eff6ff","secondaryTextColor":"#1e3a8a","secondaryBorderColor":"#93c5fd","tertiaryColor":"#ecfdf5","tertiaryTextColor":"#065f46","tertiaryBorderColor":"#86efac","lineColor":"#64748b","textColor":"#0f172a"}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Usuario
    participant App as Aplicacao cliente
    participant View as Views Razor
    participant Auth as HostedAuthOrchestrator
    participant OAuth as OAuthClientRepository
    participant Tx as HostedAuthTransactionRepository
    participant Sess as HostedAuthSessionRepository
    participant Audit as AuthAuditLog
    participant RL as HumanAuthRateLimiter
    participant Cred as UserCredentialValidator
    participant MFA as TwoFactorChallengeService
    participant Mail as Servico de email
    participant Code as AuthorizationCodeRepository
    participant Token as /api/auth/token
    participant Issuer as Emissor JWT / refresh token

    App->>App: Gerar state, nonce, code_verifier e PKCE S256
    App-->>User: Abrir login hospedado
    User->>View: GET /auth/login?response_type=code&tenant_id=...&client_id=...&redirect_uri=...&scope=...&state=...&nonce=...&code_challenge=...&code_challenge_method=S256
    Note over User,View: Authorization Request OAuth2/OIDC por query.<br/>tenant_id e uma extensao multi-tenant do produto.
    View->>OAuth: Validar tenant, cliente ativo, callback exato e scopes

    alt Entrada OAuth invalida
        OAuth-->>View: Rejeitado
        View->>Audit: hosted_authorization_rejected com correlationId
        View-->>User: Erro generico sem redirecionar
    else Entrada OAuth valida
        OAuth-->>View: Cliente autorizado
        View->>Tx: Criar transacao OAuth com tenant, client, callback, state, nonce, scope e PKCE
        View->>Sess: Criar sessao de autenticacao com TTL de 15 minutos
        View->>Audit: hosted_authorization_started
        View-->>User: Renderizar login do tenant

        Note over Tx,Sess: Transacao OAuth guarda dados do protocolo.<br/>Sessao guarda usuario, estagio, 2FA, expiracao e cancelamento.<br/>Senha nunca e armazenada.

        opt Recuperacao de senha
            User->>View: GET /auth/forgot-password?transactionId=...
            View-->>User: Formulario de recuperacao
            User->>View: POST username ou email
            View->>RL: Limitar por IP, tenant e identificador
            View->>Audit: password_recovery_requested
            alt Limite excedido
                RL-->>View: Bloqueado
                View-->>User: Resposta generica
            else Permitido
                View->>Auth: Solicitar recuperacao
                Auth->>Mail: Enviar link somente se a conta existir
                Auth-->>View: Concluido
                View-->>User: Mesma resposta para conta existente ou inexistente
                Mail-->>User: Link /reset-password
                User->>View: POST nova senha
                View->>Auth: Validar token e redefinir senha
                Auth->>Issuer: Revogar refresh tokens existentes
                Auth->>Audit: password_reset_completed
                View-->>User: Sucesso e retorno ao login
            end
        end

        User->>View: POST /auth/login com transactionId, username e senha
        View->>RL: Limitar login humano
        alt Limite de login excedido
            RL-->>View: Bloqueado
            View-->>User: Erro generico
        else Login permitido
            View->>Auth: LoginAsync
            Auth->>Audit: login_attempted com hash parcial do identificador
            Auth->>Cred: Validar senha, status e politica 2FA

            alt Credenciais ou conta invalidas
                Cred-->>Auth: Falha
                Auth->>Audit: login_failed sem motivo enumeravel
                Auth-->>View: Erro generico
                View-->>User: Login sem preservar senha
            else Credenciais validas
                Cred-->>Auth: Usuario autenticado
                Auth->>Sess: Vincular usuario e estagio sem senha
                Auth->>Audit: login_succeeded

                alt 2FA por email obrigatorio
                    Auth->>MFA: Criar challenge purpose=login e invalidar anteriores
                    MFA->>Mail: Enfileirar codigo
                    MFA-->>Auth: challenge_id, expiracao e destino mascarado
                    Auth->>Sess: Stage=AwaitingTwoFactor
                    Auth->>Audit: two_factor_sent
                    View-->>User: Renderizar 2FA

                    opt Reenvio apos cooldown
                        User->>View: POST /auth/2fa/resend
                        View->>RL: Limitar reenvio
                        alt Reenvio bloqueado
                            View-->>User: Informar espera
                        else Reenvio permitido
                            View->>MFA: Invalidar anterior e criar novo challenge
                            MFA->>Mail: Enfileirar novo codigo
                            View->>Sess: Substituir challenge ativo
                            View->>Audit: two_factor_resent
                        end
                    end

                    opt Cancelamento
                        User->>View: POST /auth/2fa/cancel
                        View->>MFA: Invalidar challenge ativo
                        View->>Sess: Limpar usuario e voltar para Login
                        View->>Audit: two_factor_cancelled
                    end

                    loop Tentativas enquanto challenge estiver pendente
                        User->>View: POST /auth/2fa com codigo
                        View->>RL: Limitar por IP, tenant e challenge
                        View->>MFA: Validar expiracao, tentativas e codigo
                        alt Codigo incorreto
                            MFA->>MFA: Incrementar tentativas atomicamente
                            View->>Audit: two_factor_failed
                            View-->>User: Erro generico
                        else Codigo expirado ou limite atingido
                            MFA->>MFA: Marcar expired ou failed
                            View->>Audit: two_factor_failed
                            View-->>User: Exigir reenvio ou reinicio
                        else Codigo correto
                            MFA->>MFA: Consumir challenge atomicamente como used
                            MFA-->>Auth: Challenge verificado
                            Auth->>Audit: two_factor_confirmed
                        end
                    end
                else 2FA nao exigido
                    Auth-->>View: Autenticacao concluida
                end

                Auth->>Sess: Transicionar atomicamente para Completing
                Auth->>Code: Criar code hash com transacao, sessao, nonce, scope, correlationId e PKCE
                Code-->>Auth: Code opaco com TTL de 60 segundos
                Auth->>Sess: Stage=Completed
                Auth->>Audit: authorization_code_issued
                View-->>User: 302 para redirect_uri com code e state
                User->>App: Callback registrado com code e state

                Note over View,App: JWT e refresh token nunca passam pela view, HTML ou URL.

                App->>Token: POST grant_type=authorization_code, code, client_id, redirect_uri e code_verifier
                Token->>Code: Validar tenant, client, callback, PKCE e consumir atomicamente
                alt Code reutilizado, expirado ou PKCE divergente
                    Code-->>Token: Rejeitado
                    Token->>Audit: authorization_code_failed
                    Token-->>App: Erro generico sem tokens
                else Code valido
                    Code-->>Token: Subject, MFA, nonce, scope e correlationId
                    Token->>Audit: authorization_code_consumed
                    Token->>Cred: Recarregar usuario, status, roles e permissoes
                    Cred-->>Token: Usuario ainda valido
                    Token->>Issuer: Emitir access token e refresh token
                    Issuer-->>Token: Tokens apos PKCE valido
                    Token-->>App: AuthTokenResponse
                end

                Note over MFA,Code: Challenges e authorization codes sao de uso unico.<br/>Reenvio invalida o challenge anterior.
                Note over App,Code: Callback, tenant, cliente, state, nonce, scope, correlationId e PKCE permanecem vinculados.
            end
        end
    end

    Note over User,Mail: Recuperacao nao revela se a conta existe.<br/>Logs nao incluem senha, codigo 2FA, code puro, code_verifier ou tokens.
